### GET all doctors filtered by specialization
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Doctors?$filter=specialization eq 'Cardiology'

### GET appointments for a specific date
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments?$filter=appointmentDate eq 2024-06-10

### POST a new patient
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Deepak",
  "lastName": "Malhotra",
  "dateOfBirth": "1992-09-25",
  "gender": "Male",
  "bloodGroup": "O+",
  "phone": "+91-9900000006",
  "email": "deepak@gmail.com",
  "address": "Bangalore",
  "emergencyContact": "+91-9900000015",
  "registrationDate": "2024-06-01"
}

### POST a new appointment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_ID": "P001",
  "doctor_ID": "DR001",
  "appointmentDate": "2024-06-20",
  "appointmentTime": "11:00:00",
  "status": "Scheduled",
  "reason": "Follow up",
  "fee": 1500.00
}

### GET patients filtered by blood group
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients?$filter=bloodGroup eq 'B+'

### PATCH appointment status to Completed
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments('A001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Completed"
}